Package com.dsi.ant.plugins.antplus.pcc.controls.defines

Enum Class AudioVideoCommandNumber

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<AudioVideoCommandNumber>
com.dsi.ant.plugins.antplus.pcc.controls.defines.AudioVideoCommandNumber
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<AudioVideoCommandNumber>, Constable
public enum AudioVideoCommandNumber extends Enum<AudioVideoCommandNumber>
Defines command numbers to use for Audio and Video control. Used in the AudioCommand and VideoCommand events, as well as the updateAudioCommandStatus and updateVideoCommandStatus commands.
